{
  "stem": "26728.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "One step might be 18 inches, the next one might be 6.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they made these inmates walk down in the quarry, bring back rocks that weighed-- marble rock that weighed as much as they could carry, 60, 70 pounds, back up these steps until they dropped.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And when they dropped, they either killed them or shoved them off into the pit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And that was just every day for the entire time, the entire life of Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And it was-- uh, it was recognized even among inmates that had been to other camps that that's the last place they wanted to go was Mauthausen if they knew anything about the camp system, which a lot them did.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They'd hear it from other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Like-- like, uh, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Wiesenthal wasn't liberated from Mauthausen, but he was in Mauthausen, and went through some of this stuff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHING] Torture chambers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had some of these devices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even worse, they had the spikes, the spiked collars and the spiked anklets made out of heavy metal, heavy wrought iron.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had, um-- they had a device.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never could figure out what the hell they used this for until a guy explained to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like you had like you're going to step on a scale, except there were no springs there, just a little metal platform.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And above this they had a device that they could crank a steel plate down to your head, like you would measure a person's height, except this was a flat piece.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a spring in there with a big piece of metal like a spike that was cocked like a spring.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they'd lower that down onto this inmate's head and fire it like a mousetrap.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that spike would go in their brain.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
